        reason: 'Al-Biruni preserves the electional horoscope cast for Baghdad in his Chronology of Ancient Nations (al-Athar al-Baqiya, c. 1000 CE), recording the planetary positions used to fix the foundation moment. The chart is detailed enough that modern historians of science (Kennedy and Pingree, The Astrological History of Masha\'allah, 1971) reconstruct it and confirm a date of 30–31 July 762 CE, settling both the event and its astronomically derived date.',
