          name: 'The Pentagon Papers (Gravel Edition), Vol. 3, Ch. 2: "The Gulf of Tonkin." Beacon Press, 1971.',
          url: 'https://www.mtholyoke.edu/acad/intrel/pentagon3/pent4.html',
